{
  "text": "In certain respects, this method is a systematic form of expert judgment since experts often match similar project(s) from their own experiences in order to determine the appropriate effort estimates [CITATION_1] . Estimation requires the comparability of structures of the project that has to be calculated and completed software developments serving as analogy groundwork [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
